data.description: **UTILITIES ASSESSMENT PAID OFF BY SELLER!** Looking for a OPEN FLOOR PLAN 3 bedroom/2 bath home with PRIVATE DEN/OFFICE (Could be used as a 4th Bedroom)? NOT in a Flood Zone! NEW ROOF & Hot water heater, A/C 2 Years Old. Spacious Living Area with Vaulted Ceilings and Open Concept Kitchen with extra counter top space on the Island and Separate Pantry. Master Bedroom boasts a Oversized Walk-In Closet with Master Bathroom featuring Separate Corner Garden Tub and Shower. All Carpet was replaced in 2021. This home offers New Gutters and hurricane shutters.   Have a Green Thumb....Vegetable Garden Beds and Banana Trees in Your Backyard Oasis, as you relax inside the screened in Lanai off the back of the home. House is the highest point on the street, fire station less than a mile away and a fire hydrant in the front yard, which means discounted insurance. You will have quick access to shopping, restaurants, and schools near and around Pine Island Rd, Santa Barbara Blvd, Nicholas Pkwy, and Hancock Bridge Pkwy. Also conveniently located 3 miles from Matlacha Island! Don't Miss Your Opportunity to be the proud owner of this beautiful home. INFORMATION IS DEEMED RELIABLE BUT NOT GUARANTEED…TO BE VERIFIED BY THE BUYER AND/OR BUYER'S AGENT.
